'''卡尔尼科巴语'''是在[[印度|印度]][[尼科巴群岛|尼科巴群岛]]使用得最广的[[尼科巴语支|尼科巴语支]]语言。

尽管和[[越南语|越南语]]和[[高棉语|高棉语]]是远亲，其更可能和临近的[[南岛语系|南岛语系]]语言如[[尼亚斯语|尼亚斯语]]和[[亚齐语|亚齐语]]有关，它们同属一个[[语言联盟|语言联盟]]。<ref>Cysouw, Michael; [http://email.eva.mpg.de/~cysouw/pdf/cysouwDGFS2005.pdf Quantitative explorations of the world-wide distribution of rare characteristics, or: the exceptionality of north-western European languages] {{Wayback|url=http://email.eva.mpg.de/~cysouw/pdf/cysouwDGFS2005.pdf |date=20090514195944 }}; pp. 11-12</ref>

卡尔尼科巴语是[[动宾主语序|动宾主语序]]语言，一定程度上是[[黏着语|黏着语]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://wals.info/languoid/lect/wals_code_nca |title=WALS: Nicobarese |access-date=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204054905/https://wals.info/languoid/lect/wals_code_nca |dead-url=no }}</ref>其有相当复杂的动词[[后缀|后缀]]系统和一些[[中缀|中缀]]，如不同的属格助词和“疑问”语气的名词和代词。<ref>Whitehead, Rev. G.; ''Dictionary of the Car （Nicobarese） language''; published 1925 by American Baptist Mission Press; pp. ''xxvi''-''xxxii''</ref>

